target:
Distributing game software through the internet without permission from the rights holder,
or downloading illegally distributed software through the internet is strictly prohibited.

The English translation patch is currently a work in progress and there will be
inaccuracies and potential bugs.

We ask for your understanding and cooperation.
Translation Notes:
Leaving this here just in case we put out any updated preview releases in the future:

This is a UI only preview build of the Starlit Season English Translation Patch.
This preview build is currently tested to work with version 1.10 of Starlit Season on Steam,
and is not complete, nor is it guaranteed to work on pirated copies.

This work in progress patch features a roughly 95% complete UI translation, however
the story and all COMMU events are not complete.

The game can be played from start to finish with this patch, however there are still
outstanding issues that still need to be addressed, which includes but is not limited to
text overflow, preliminary translations, awkward sentence structure, etc.

We can only give an estimated timeframe of "when it's done".  We thank you for your
patience and understanding.

-NG
